Installation:
    brew install wget
    brew install ag
    brew install python3
    pip3 install powerline-status
    git clone git@github.com:rstratton/.vim.git ~/.vim
    cd ~/.vim
    ./install.sh

Submodule Installation:
    cd ~/.vim
    mkdir -p ~/.vim/bundle
    git submodule add http://github.com/<github_acct>/<plugin>.git bundle/<plugin_name>
    git add .
    git commit -m "Install <plugin> as a submodule."

Submodule Removal (from http://stackoverflow.com/a/1260982):
    1) Delete the relevant section from the .gitmodules file.
    2) Stage the .gitmodules changes (git add .gitmodules)
    3) Delete the relevant section from ".git/config".
    4) Run "git rm --cached path_to_submodule" (no trailing slash).
    5) Run "rm -rf .git/modules/path_to_submodule"
    6) Commit 'git commit -m "Removed submodule <name>"'
    7) Delete the now untracked submodule files
    8) "rm -rf path_to_submodule"
